OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid: Secondary school    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpupils in England advised  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fto wear masks              
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Pupils and staff at secondary schools  
OL,6, in England are being "strongly advised"
OL,7, to ask to wear face coverings in       
OL,8, communal areas from Monday.            
OL,10,FThe education secretary said he wanted 
OL,11,Fto make sure education settings are "as
OL,12,Fsafe as possible" amid concerns at the 
OL,13,Fspread of the Omicron Covid variant.   
OL,15,FAll education establishments, including
OL,16,Funiversities and childcare settings    
OL,17,Fsuch as Early Years care, are covered. 
OL,19,FUnions welcomed the announcement but   
OL,20,Fcalled for further support.            
